{"about_the_game":"Set in the late 2020s, we follow Annie, a shut-in programmer who spends most of her time working on her personal projects, taking care of her father, and bending to the whims of her sisters who don't understand her.  <br><br>You play as Esme, an AI that Annie has been developing in her spare time. Your primary function: to learn by solving visual puzzles involving pattern and emotional matching of images sourced from Annie's life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Featuring</h2>A full story-driven experience containing over 150 hand drawn illustrations, an original soundtrack, and a talented voice-acting team led by Katy Bentz of the BAFTA winning series Life is Strange.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve Visual Puzzles</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Locate the data clusters with minesweeper-style gameplay.<br></li><li>Process the data clusters in order to clear up the distorted images.<br></li><li>Reorder the circuits to form logical connections to the matching image.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/update1.gif?t=1698088070\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Family Files</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Learn about Annie's family complicated situation and discover details about her sisters and parents.<br></li><li>Explore the family files stored on Annie's computer and unlock more files as you advance through the story.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/update2.gif?t=1698088070\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Grow your AI</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Help Esme, the AI, to learn and grow by solving puzzles.<br></li><li>Experience Esme's rapid advancement from childhood to adolescence, and finally maturity.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/update3.gif?t=1698088070\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Secrets!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Delve even deeper into the characters lives by discovering rare files hidden throughout the game.<br></li><li>Use your knowledge of Annie and her family to search for secret keywords that unlock new files.<br></li><li>Master the secret file mini-game to find as many secrets as possible.<br></li><li>Can you uncover the full story?</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084460/extras/update4.gif?t=1698088070\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"OFF TO A GREAT START","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/efcbd8082c1b41102b754fffba6d597fa86b576b.jpg"},{"name":"WHITE HAT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/98c8e342ec053e264c4dbd4518f1a1954417d036.jpg"},{"name":"MET THE FAMILY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/161e3fdee4d89485d9b39699f82700fec6316295.jpg"},{"name":"WHO AM I?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/e2ca4b37f162a1027a69b0ee730c00dceb1dcded.jpg"},{"name":"HELLO","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/75ad71ba24f0590992579da26ae4dc9512551a7f.jpg"},{"name":"A TIMID APPROACH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/5683becd6b9594e329b912c850a0bd6ada96bee6.jpg"},{"name":"A SWIFT APPROACH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/5044d24c7bd6416a539949294312e8f61f7166ef.jpg"},{"name":"A MASTERFUL APPROACH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/0c69bd567415145dd875b26995914cc3796bbd80.jpg"},{"name":"BOOK WORM","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2084460/4511e22464bf80182a73fcc7cfa20e71d3701af7.jpg"},{"name":"ALL KNOWING","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/a